<h3 class=3D"text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">3.3 Controles de=
 c=C3=A1mara</h3>
<ul class=3D"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:l=
ast-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-co=
l gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Orbit</strong> (de=
fault): girar alrededor del centro de la granja.</li>
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Isometric snap</st=
rong>: bot=C3=B3n para vista isom=C3=A9trica 45=C2=B0 (como el plano de Cop=
ilot).</li>
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>First person</stro=
ng>: caminar por la granja (WASD + mouse).</li>
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Camera POV</strong=
>: click en una c=C3=A1mara =E2=86=92 ver lo que ve esa c=C3=A1mara (posici=
=C3=B3n + FOV).</li>
</ul>
<h3 class=3D"text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">3.4 Capas toggle=
 (equivalentes al 2D)</h3>
<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading=
-[1.7]">Mismo sistema de capas que el SVG: terreno, zonas, edificios, valla=
s, equipamiento, c=C3=A1maras, animales, sensores, alertas, trayectorias. T=
oggle independiente de cada capa.</p>
<h3 class=3D"text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">3.5 Datos en tie=
mpo real</h3>
<ul class=3D"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:l=
ast-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-co=
l gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Animales:</strong>=
 WebSocket desde seedy-backend =E2=86=92 posiciones YOLO tracking =E2=86=92=
 actualizar sprites cada frame.</li>
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Sensores:</strong>=
 MQTT via WebSocket =E2=86=92 InfluxDB =E2=86=92 actualizar colores/valores=
.</li>
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Alertas:</strong> =
MQTT =E2=86=92 mostrar marcadores parpadeantes en la zona afectada.</li>
</ul>
